Mr. Barnes waives his right to Preliminary Hearing; the Court accepts this waiver and binds him over for Arraignment.
State files information; Arraignment:--service of Information admitted, reading waived--maximum penalties recited

--No contact with Donald Gigante or Nancy Rettschlag
--No presence at W6420 County Trunk A in Town of Milford

--To obtain/maintain employment and/or education program, per Agent
--To pay statutory costs, fees and surcharges
